script.sh     Perform all steps to configure the Spectrum Scale for demo purposes


script.sh executes the following scripts:

Configure the Spectrum Scale filesystem for demo purposes:
script-01.sh  Show Spectrum Scale filesystems
script-02.sh  Add second storage pool to filesystem fs1
script-03.sh  Create placement policy for filesystem fs1
script-04.sh  - TODO: Placeholder for migration policies -
script-05.sh  Create filesets and some example data
script-06.sh  Create snapshot for fileset snapshots
script-07.sh  - TODO: Placeholder for snapshot schedule -

Tweak the configuration to show more management capabilities:
script-80.sh  Authorize the default GUI admin to manage ACLs
script-81.sh  Trigger health events by filesets that exceed thresholds
script-99.sh  Update the capacitiy reports
